fabric-adorned%20masterpiece%20still%20lives%20at%20my%20parents'%20house%2C%20tucked%20away%20in%20a%20cabinet%20among%20photo%20albums%20and%20newspaper%20clippings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20pulled%20it%20out%20not%20long%20ago%20and%20flipped%20through%20the%20pages.%20Twelve-year-old%20me%20imagined%20I'd%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgraduate-school-masters-mba-college-regret-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ego%20to%20grad%20school%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20become%20a%20journalist%20(check%20and%20check).%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20accurately%20I%20saw%20myself%2C%20even%20at%20a%20young%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20I%20came%20to%20my%20projections%20page%2C%20where%20I%20mused%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdidnt-know-wanted-kids-having-one-changed-everything-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elike%20to%20have%20children%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20to%20get%20married.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20now%2027%20years%20later%2C%20and%20not%20much%20has%20changed.%20As%20I%20prepare%20to%20enter%20my%2040s%2C%20I've%20had%20moments%20of%20the%20proverbial%20%26quot%3Bbaby%20fever%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20always%20fades.%20I'm%20an%20introvert%20who's%20solidly%20protective%20of%20my%20solo%20time%2C%20and%20I%20always%20assumed%20that%20meant%20that%20all%20manner%20of%20parenting%20would%20be%20a%20no-go%20for%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20you%20can%20imagine%20my%20surprise%20when%20I%20met%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-stepmom-first-and-it-made-me-a-better-mom-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20now-stepdaughter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20and