usband%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20expected%20to%20do%20hands-on%20parenting%20if%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20%E2%80%94%20I%20embraced%20my%20new%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229efa676c-4f9f-43e9-939c-2fe27977bebc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EParenting%20has%20expanded%20my%20life%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20enjoy%20so%20many%20things%20about%20parenting.%20I'm%20more%20present%20in%20my%20life%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20her%20excitement%20during%20new%20experiences.%20I'm%20more%20involved%20in%20my%20community%20because%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20she's%20exposed%20to%20as%20many%20things%20as%20possible.%20I'm%20more%20patient%20and%20thoughtful%20because%20I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20good%20example.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20been%20amazing%20to%20watch%20my%20family%20welcome%20her%20and%20see%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funaffectionate-parents-affectionate-grandparents-hug-confusing-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eparents%20become%20grandparents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I've%20developed%20new%20friendships%20with%20moms%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20otherwise%3B%20as%20much%20as%20we%20want%20to%20believe%20that%20friendships%20can%20transcend%20circumstance%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20fact%20that%20you're%20more%20exposed%20to%20people%20in%20the%20same%20season%20of%20life%20as%20you.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20a%20friend%20asked%20me%20what%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpay-cut-childcare-budget-decision-challenges-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echildcare%20responsibilities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%2C%20and%20I%20rattled%20off%20some%20things%3A%20I%20pack%20school%20lunches%2C%20plan%20playdates%20and%20sleepovers%2C%20figure%20out%20our%20travel%20schedule%2C%20and%20h