%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20rollout%20of%20a%20few%20generative%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20bank's%20wealth-management%20division%2C%20and%20has%20more%20use%20cases%20in%20the%20pipeline%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20bank's%20push%20into%20generative%20AI%20has%20been%20fueled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorgan-stanley-picks-new-head-innovation-sean-manahan-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20early%20partnership%20with%20ChatGPT-maker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20coincides%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-goldman-jpmorgan-bridgewater-using-ai-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street's%20recent%20obsession%20with%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20boost%20productivity%20and%20reduce%20grunt%20work%20for%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcMillan%20encourages%20employees%20to%20pitch%20new%20AI%20solutions.%20His%20firmwide%20team%20acts%20as%20a%20filter%20and%20vets%20the%20ideas%2C%20which%20can%20come%20from%20practically%20anyone%20who's%20done%20the%20required%20training%20at%20the%20bank.%20To%20avoid%20creating%20an%20unruly%20situation%20where%20thousands%20of%20technologists%2C%20analysts%2C%20and%20bankers%20are%20building%20their%20own%20AI%20tools%2C%20he's%20devised%20a%20rigorous%20multi-step%20process%20that%20involves%20pitching%20solutions%20to%20some%20of%20the%20firm's%20top%20execs%20and%20devising%20a%20business%20value%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20role%2C%20McMillan%20co-chairs%20an%20AI%20steering%20group%20formalized%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20with%20Global%20Director%20of%20Research%20Katy%20Huberty.%20The%20steering%20committee%2C%20which%20has%20representatives%20from%20each%20department%2C%20vets%20all%20AI%20use%20cases%20pitched%20by%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20steering%20group%20is%20working%20through%20more%20than%2030%20use%20cases%20that%20are%20in%20various%20stages%20on%20the%20way%20to%20launch%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20McMillan%20said.%20AskResearch%2C%20an%20assistant%20that%20gives%20investment%20bankers%2C%20salespeople%2C%20and%20traders%20information%20found%20buried%20in%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20research%20reports%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20generative%20AI%20product%20to%20make%20it%20through%20the%20process%20since%20launching%20McMillan's%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20pitches%20the%20steering%20committee%20sees%20fall%20into%20two%20buckets%3A%20use%20cases%20that%20are%20relevant%20to%20several%20groups%2C%20or%20that%20matter%20to%20a%20specific%20team%20or%20group%20of%20users.%20For%20the%20former%2C%20McMillan%20is%20able%20to%20coordinate%20teams%20across%20the%20firm%20to%20collaborate%20and%20build%20solutions%20together%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20increasing%20reusability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20structuring%20the%20AI%20approval%20process%20this%20way%2C%20McMillan%20hopes%20to%20enable%20the%20bank%20to%20innovate%20without%20sacrificing%20safety.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20there%20might%20be%20creative%20tension%20between%20experimentation%20and%20process%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20a%20rigorous%20process%20will%20ultimately%20allow%20us%20to%20develop%20and%20deploy%20technology%20faster%20and%20more%20efficiently%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e6a7ddc-8116-4a7f-bceb-6dc8b0fb1ac1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20the%208-step%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20pitching%20AI%20solutions%20is%20open%20to%20anyone%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20there%20is%20some%20leg%20work%20involved.%20Mainly%2C%20workers%20have%20to%20complete%20specific%20training%20on%20governance%20and%20AI%20principles%20and%20meet%20standards%20around%20information%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20steering%20group%20meets%20every%20other%20week%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20pitches%2C%20usually%20going%20through%20five%20or%20six%20proposals.%20The%20steering%20group%20usually%20either%20approves%20or%20approves%20with%20conditions%2C%20like%20rethinking%20an%20aspect%20of%20the%20solution%20or%20coming%20together%20with%20other%20teams%20that%20pitched%20similar%20ideas.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20pitches%20are%20rejected%20%E2%80%94%20something%20McMillan%20says%20he%20generally%20tries%20not%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20position%20where%20I'm%20telling%20people%20no.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20people%20yes%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20get%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20presentations%20that%20are%20approved%2C%20the%20next%20steps%20typically%20involve%20identifying%20the%20people%20who%20will%20execute%20and%20figuring%20out%20who%20from%20tech%2C%20legal%2C%20compliance%2C%20and%20risk%20needs%20to%20be%20involved.%20Workers%20going%20through%20this%20process%20also%20have%20to%20articulate%20deliverables%20and%20identify%20the%20risks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20having%20a%20plan%20for%20mitigating%20those%20risks.%20That%20might%20be%20a%20standard%20set%20of%20questions%20and%20answers%20used%20in%20testing%20or%20making%20certain%20teams%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20also%20have%20to%20put%20together%20a%20business%20value%20proposition%20that%20outlines%20the%20benefits%2C%20which%20could%20be%20quantifiable%2C%20such%20as%20decreasing%20margin%20or%20operating%20costs%2C%20finding%20new%20revenue%20streams%2C%20or%20decreasing%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20other%20week%2C%20the%20AI%20steering%20committee%20meets%20to%20review%20the%20status%20of%20these%20projects.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20process%2C%20the%20group%20pitching%20presents%20a%20final%20time%20to%20the%20steering%20group%20for%20go-live%20approval%20to%20ensure%20all%20the%20conditions%20are%20met.%20Finally%2C%20use%20cases%20go%20into%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20doing%20is%20we're%