2_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20remotely%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20going%20to%20do%20great%20work%2C%20and%20people%20are%20going%20to%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20you%20need%20to%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20do%20great%20work%2C%20and%20I%20need%20to%20tell%20people%20about%20the%20work%20I'm%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20having%20a%20big%20mental%20shift%20in%20my%20career%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20responsibility%20and%20own%20it.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20expect%20my%20manager%2C%20who%20has%20a%20ton%20on%20their%20plate%20and%20a%20lot%20going%20on%2C%20to%20always%20be%20the%20one%20checking%20in%20on%20me.%20Instead%2C%20I%20need%20to%20advocate%20for%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20scheduling%20regular%20touchpoints%20with%20your%20manager%20so%20they%20understand%20the%20value%20you're%20providing%20to%20the%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20something%20harder%20to%20see%20when%20you%20work%20remotely.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20work%20from%20home%2C%20you%20need%20to%20overcompensate%20to%20combat%20this.%20When%20in%20person%2C%20people%20can%20see%20that%20you're%20working%20and%20can%20ask%20you%20questions%20without%20friction.%20To%20ensure%20your%20manager%20doesn't%20think%20you're%20slacking%20off%2C%20send%20snippets%20on%20Fridays%20that%20include%20everything%20you%20did%20that%20week%20and%20your%20priorities%20for%20next%20week.%20Also%2C%20send%20no-update%20updates%2C%20which%20update%20stakeholders%20on%20where%20things%20stand%20without%20them%20asking%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20way%2C%20they're%20always%20aware%20of%20what%20you've%20done%20and%20what's%20coming%20next.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20provide%20feedback%2C%20you've%20given%20them%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-get-passed-up-promotions-from-google-recr