anding%20the%20immigration%20court%20system%2C%20which%20has%20been%20experiencing%20backlogs%20for%20years.%20That's%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20price%20tag%20of%20deporting%20millions%20of%20people%20and%20losing%20out%20on%20tax%20revenue%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanimmigrationcouncil.org%2Fresearch%2Fmass-deportation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Immigration%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimated%20it%20would%20cost%20the%20federal%20government%20over%20%24315%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20process%20would%20be%20incredibly%20tricky%20to%20navigate%20legally.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20you%20arrest%20the%20wrong%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20pointed%20out.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20US%2C%20if%20you%20arrest%20the%20wrong%20people%20and%20subject%20them%20to%20inappropriate%20and%20unpleasant%20treatment%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20damages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20don't%20understand%20how%20that%20would%20work%20within%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20environment%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20too%20early%20to%20predict%20how%20Trump's%20policies%20will%20pan%20out%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20Johnson%20is%20seeing%20drastic%20barriers%20to%20Trump's%20tariff%20and%20immigration%20plans.%20Not%20only%20are%20they%20undesirable%20policies%20for%20the%20economy%20and%20American%20consumers%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20unfeasible%20to%20carry%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20Trump%20go%20through%20with%20his%20tariff%20and%20immigration%20policies%2C%20it'll%20be%20up%20to%20the%20American%20people%20to%20judge%20their%20efficacy%20and%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20change%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20about%20American%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we'll%20see%20how%20people%20feel%20about%20that%20in%20the%20midterm%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E