2C%20and%20not%20President-elect%20Trump's%2C%20had%20been%20the%20aberration%2C%20and%20that%20relations%20with%20the%20US%20are%20about%20to%20get%20a%20whole%20lot%20rockier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorld%20leaders%20who%20attended%20the%20summits%20made%20clear%20they%20were%20bracing%20for%20dramatic%20policy%20shifts%20from%20the%20White%20House%2C%20especially%20on%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Even%20leaders%20who%20align%20ideologically%20with%20Trump%20seemed%20shaken%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20upheaval%20that%20may%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20potential%20US%20disengagement%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20all%20we%20can%20to%20prevent%20the%20western%20front%20from%20fraying%2C%26quot%3B%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20told%20reporters%20in%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20everyone%20realizes%20where%20the%20truth%20lies%20in%20the%20Ukrainian%20conflict%20and%20Russia's%20responsibility%20in%20not%20wanting%20to%20engage%20in%20dialog.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20approach%20to%20the%20summit%20had%20the%20air%20of%20a%20popular%20elder%20statesman%20saying%20his%20last%20goodbyes.%20He%20never%20took%20questions%20from%20the%20press%2C%20and%20limited%20himself%20at%20the%20G-20%20meeting%20to%20brief%20public%20remarks.%20Cameras%20caught%20him%20backslapping%20and%20hugging%20fellow%20leaders%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20presumably%20seeing%20him%20for%20the%20last%20time%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvidence%20that%20Biden's%20team%20wasn't%20up%20for%20a%20fight%20was%20everywhere.%20Brazil%20declined%20to%20invite%20Ukraine's%20leader%2C%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%2C%20to%20the%20event%2C%20and%20the%20G-20's%20final%20communique%20was%20rammed%20through%20by%20the%20host%2C%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%2C%20despite%20opposition%20from%20other%20nations%20over%20the%20weakness%20of%20its%20language%20on%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20know%2C%20this%20is%20my%20last%20G-20%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20had%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20G-20%20summit's%20first%20day.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20made%20progress%20together%2C%20but%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20keep%20going%20-%20and%20I'm%20sure%20you%20will%2C%20regardless%20of%20my%20urging%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20after%20discussing%20climate%20finance%2C%20Biden%20cut%20himself%20off.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20much%20more%20to%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20pool%20report.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20refusal%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20news%20of%20the%20day%20also%20meant%20that%20he%20never%20provided%20a%20justification%20or%20explanation%20for%20one%20of%20the%20last%20foreign-policy%20decisions%20of%20his%20presidency%3A%20allowing%20Ukraine%20to%20fire%20long-range%20US-provided%20ATACMS%20missiles%20into%20Russian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20decision%20came%20to%20light%20on%20Sunday.%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20made%20clear%20a%20day%20later%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20follow%20Biden's%20example%20and%20that%20Berlin%20would%20continue%20to%20refuse%20to%20supply%20its%20Taurus%20missile%20system%20to%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Tuesday%2C%20Ukraine%20had%20fired%20ATACMS%20at%20an%20ammunition%20depot%20in%20Russia's%20Bryansk%20border%20region%2C%20though%20it%20didn't%20officially%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20US%20weapon%20was%20used.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20announced%20that%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20had%20signed%20off%20on%20a%20revised%20nuclear%20doctrine%20that%20lowered%20the%20threshold%20for%20Russia%20to%20resort%20to%20using%20the%20weapons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20ATACMS%20represented%20%26quot%3Ba%20qualitatively%20new%20phase%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20war%2C%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20told%20a%20news%20briefing%20in%20Rio%2C%20addressing%20reporters%20in%20English%20on%20the%20question.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20will%20react%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20presidency%20-%20and%20for%20decades%20before%20as%20a%20US%20senator%20and%20vice%20president%20-%20Biden%20had%20set%20his%20aides%20on%20edge%20with%20off-the-cuff%20remarks%20and%20verbal%20gaffes.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20resisted%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20President%2C%20why%20did%20you%20change%20your%20mind%20on%20Ukraine%20shooting%20long-range%20missiles%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20reporter%20shouted%20to%20Biden%20during%20a%20camera%20spray%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20he%20met%20Lula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20appeared%20ready%20to%20respond%20but%20then%20decided%20to%20keep%20the%20silence%20he%20has%20largely%20maintained%20in%20the%20two%20weeks%20since%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20lost%20the%20US%20election%20to%20Trump.%20Instead%2C%20US%20adversaries%20including%20China%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20allied%20leaders%20such%20as%20Scholz%20have%20filled%20the%20vacuum%20left%20by%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20clear%20in%20my%20talks%20with%20Xi%20that%20we%20won't%20accept%20weapons%20deliveries%20to%20Russia%20and%20that%20we%20will%20look%20even%20closer%20to%20dual-use%20goods%20for%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20Scholz%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Lavrov%20spoke%2C%20Biden%20joined%20other%20world%20leaders%20for%20a%20G-20%20group%20photograph.%20Cameras%20showed%20him%20coughing%20into%20his%20fist%20and%20unwrapping%20a%20throat%20lozenge.%20Biden%2C%20who%20looked%20stiff%20and%20walked%20haltingly%20all%20week%2C%20turns%2082%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photo%20opportunity%20was%20a%20redo%20from%20the%20summit's%20first%20day%2C%20when%20Biden%20along%20with%20Canada's%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Italy's%20Meloni%20had%20missed%20the%20traditional%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20photo.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20intensified%20grumbling%20from%20White%20House%20staffers%20already%20irked%20by%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20chaotic%20organization%20from%20the%20summit%20hosts.%20Journalists%20peppered%20Brazilian%20officials%20about%20the%20decision%20to%20take%20the%20photo%20without%20the%20US%20president%20-%20something%20unthinkable%20at%20any%20previous%20G-20%20summit%2C%20and%20all%20the%20more%20for%20a%20leader%20making%20his%20swan-song%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrazil%20is%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Communications%20Minister%20Paulo%20Pimenta%20explained%2C%20according%20to%20a%20pool%20report.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20it's%20time%2C%20it's%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20one%20more%20foreign%20trip%20-%20to%20Angola%20next%20month%20-%20before%20he%20leaves%20office.%20Even%20allies%20seemed%20to%20recognize%20that%20it's%20time%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20changing%20so%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20European%20Commission%20President%20Ursula%20Von%20Der%20Leyen%20said%20in%20a%20post%20to%20X%20that%20featured%20a%20photo%20of%20her%20with%20Biden%20and%20Xi.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20is%20good%20to%20see%20familiar%20faces%20in%20these%20global%20summits.%20To%20greet%20fellow%20G20%20leaders.%20And%20welcome%20new%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732092120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fjkd89p38_joe-biden-_625x300_20_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstory-behind-joe-bidens-viral-fade-out-into-amazon-rainforest-7062059%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20years%20ago%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20declared%20%26quot%3BAmerica's%20back%26quot%3B%20and%20told%20his%20fellow%20world%20leaders%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20been%20an%20aberration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F