ent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20nine%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20voted%20in%20bypolls%20today%2C%20the%20BJP%20urged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20properly%20check%20the%20identity%20of%20voters%20clad%20in%20burqa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20BJP's%20Akhilesh%20Kumar%20Awasthi%20said%20there%20have%20past%20cases%20of%20veiled%20women%20trying%20to%20cast%20votes%20multiple%20times.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20some%20men%20have%20worn%20burqa%20and%20tried%20to%20vote.%20On%20many%20occasions%2C%20they%20have%20been%20stopped%20by%20poll%20officials.%20if%20the%20identity%20of%20burqa-clad%20women%20is%20not%20checked%2C%20fake%20voting%20will%20take%20place.%20Only%20proper%20checking%20will%20ensure%20fair%20and%20transparent%20voting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20adequate%20number%20of%20women%20cops%20must%20be%20deployed%20at%20polling%20stations%20to%20ensure%20proper%20checking%20of%20burqa-clad%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20flagged%20cases%20of%20cops%20checking%20voter%20ID%20cards.%20Party%20chief%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20two%20cops%20asking%20for%20voters'%20identity%20cards%20and%20sought%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Election%20Commission%20exists%2C%20it%20must%20come%20alive%20and%20ensure%20that%20cops%20do%20not%20check%20IDs%2C%20roads%20are%20not%20shut%2C%20IDs%20are%20not%20seized%2C%20voters%20are%20not%20threatened%2C%20pace%20of%20voting%20is%20not%20slowed%20down%2C%20time%20is%20not%20wasted%20and%20the%20administration%20does%20not%20become%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Kanpur%20police%20responded%20to%20the%20post%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20officers%20concerned%20have%20been%20suspended.%20State%20police%20comes%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20during%20polls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20also%20said%20anyone%20who%20went%20home%20without%20voting%20after%20being%20stopped%20by%20cops%20must%20go%20back%20and%20cast%20his%2Fher%20vote.%20%26quot%3BNow%20no%20irregularity%20will%20happen.%20If%20someone%20stops%20you%2C%20inform%20poll%20officials%20or%20political%20party%20members%20there.%20%26quot%3BGo%20fearlessly%20and%20make%20sure%20you%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20Assembly%20seats%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20--%20Katehari%2C%20Karhal%2C%20Mirapur%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Majhawan%2C%20Sisamau%2C%20Khair%2C%20Phulpur%20and%20Kundarki%20--%20are%20voting%20in%20the%20bypolls%20today.%20These%20seats%20were%20vacated%20after%20the%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20were%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732090860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frsa6m0vo_up-bypolls_625x300_20_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-bypolls-akhilesh-yadav-up-polls-bjp-flags-burqa-voters-samajwadi-party-says-cops-cant-check-id-7062350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20nine%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20voted%20in%20bypolls%20today%2C%20the%20BJP%20urged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20properly%20check%20the%20identity%20of%20voters%20clad%20in%20burqa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-bypolls-akhilesh-yadav-up-polls-bjp-flags-burqa-voters-samajwadi-party-says-cops-cant-check-id-7062350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GDP%20growth%20likely%20to%20slip%20to%206.5%25%2C%20FY25%20growth%20estimate%20at%207%25%3A%20ICRA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732090813000%2C%