20make%20travel%20easier%20for%20everyone.%20A%20prime%20example%20is%20the%20revamped%20Mo%20Bus%20app%2C%20which%20simplifies%20commuting%20by%20helping%20users%20locate%20nearby%20bus%20stops%20within%20500%20metres%2C%20plan%20journeys%2C%20and%20track%20buses%20in%20real-time%2C%20including%20details%20like%20arrival%20times%20and%20bus%20occupancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20added%20convenience%2C%20users%20can%20purchase%20digital%20tickets%20and%20mobile%20bus%20passes%20directly%20through%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECRUT%20has%20also%20pioneered%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20disaggregated%20ticketing%20system%20that%20collects%20passenger%20data%20by%20gender%2C%20age%2C%20and%20disability%20to%20enable%20more%20informed%20decision-making.%20This%20system%20identifies%20travel%20patterns%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20peak%20travel%20times%2C%20preferred%20modes%20of%20transport%2C%20and%20popular%20routes%20%E2%80%94%20allowing%20CRUT%20to%20tailor%20services%20to%20better%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20women%20and%20other%20demographics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20data%20can%20guide%20adjustments%20to%20bus%20schedules%2C%20increase%20frequency%20on%20popular%20routes%2C%20or%20assign%20female%20conductors%20for%20added%20safety%2C%20ensuring%20that%20public%20transport%20remains%20both%20responsive%20and%20inclusive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20city%20is%20also%20home%20to%20the%20Babasaheb%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20Bus%20Terminal%20(BSABT)%2C%20connecting%20Odisha%20through%20both%20interstate%20and%20intrastate%20bus%20routes.%20With%2044%20bus%20bays%2C%20six%20city%20service%20bays%2C%20and%20parking%20for%20111%20buses%2C%20it%20accommodates%20over%2030%2C000%20passengers%20daily%2C%20making%20it%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20transport%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3