D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalbari%2C%20a%20suburb%20in%20the%20picturesque%20city%2C%20has%20remained%20home%20to%20a%20sizable%20population%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343165%2Fchennai-street-dogs-shelter-for-paraplegic-abandoned-disabled-sarah-iyer-madras-animal-rescue-society%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estray%20animals%2C%20who%20often%20seek%20food%20and%20shelter%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes.%20Chandrika%20soon%20realised%20that%20many%20of%20the%20strays%20she%20encountered%20were%20suffering%20from%20serious%20illnesses%20and%20injuries%2C%20which%20were%20often%20left%20untreated%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20or%20awareness%20in%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20her%20own%20hands%2C%20creating%20what%20would%2C%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20become%20her%20rescue%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20relief%20centre%20%E2%80%94%20Indie%20RTR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20an%20NGO%20or%20a%20relief%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrika%20clarifies%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20to%20rescue%2C%20treat%20and%20release%20the%20stray%20animals%20we%20encounter%20back%20to%20the%20location%20we%20brought%20them%20from.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20funds%2C%20Chandrika%20relies%20on%20family%20and%20friends%20and%20avoids%20appealing%20for%20monetary%20support.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20approach%20me%2C%20wanting%20to%20donate%20food%2C%20rice%2C%20or%20other%20items%20for%20the%20dogs.%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20receive%20these%20contributions%20in%20kind%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20not%20to%20accept%20cash%20donations.%20I%20have%20seen%20a%20lot