%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20her%20on%20the%20street%2C%20I%20was%20out%20for%20my%20usual%20morning%20walk%20at%205%20am%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mani%20Chhetri%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20her%20many%20times%20before%2C%20helping%20every%20dog%20she%20came%20across.%20She%20would%20feed%20them%2C%20treat%20them%2C%20and%20do%20everything%20on%20her%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20was%20thoroughly%20impressed%20by%20the%20compassion%20one%20woman%20could%20show%20and%20the%20resolve%20with%20which%20she%20continued%20her%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20dog%20was%20sick%20or%20injured%2C%20whether%20from%20an%20accident%20or%20something%20else%2C%20she%20would%20take%20care%20of%20them.%20From%20my%20heart%2C%20I%20felt%20she%20was%20doing%20something%20really%20special%20for%20these%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-500x643.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Chandrika%20and%20her%20small%20team%20caters%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20dogs%20all%20across%20the%20city%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-500x643.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-233x300.jpg%20233w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191-150x193.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FtempImagenE0fBq-1731659191.jpg%20712w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22643%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Chandrika%20and%20her%20small%20team%20caters%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20dogs%20all%20across%20the%20city%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20with%20Chandrika%2C%20Mani%20came%20to%20know%20that%20she%20was%20renting%20a%20place%20to%20cater%20to%20numerous%20dogs%20that%20needed%20special%20care.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20help.%E2%80%99%20So%2C%20I%20offered%20her%20a%20space%20on%20my%20premises%20for%20the%20rescue%20centre.%20It%E2%80%99s%20heartwarming%20to%20see%20that%20while%20she%20is%20doing%20something%20good%2C%20she%20is%20also%20receiving%20help.%20If%20you%20have%20humanity%2C%20you%20will%20always%20want%20to%20help%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20and%20her%20group%20of%20supporters%20cater%20to%20stray%20dogs%20across%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20call%20we%20get%2C%20we%20immediately%20send%20someone%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20dog.%20Treat%20them%20here%2C%20and%20release%20them%20back%20in%20the%20location%20once%20they%E2%80%99ve%20recovered%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrika%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20gym%E2%80%99s%20unique%20initiative%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrika%E2%80%99s%20work%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20unnoticed%20by%20the%20local%20community.%20Among%20the%20supporters%20of%20her%20efforts%20are%20Alok%20Menon%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Shilpa%2C%20owners%20of%20a%20nearby%20gym.%20After%20having%20opened%20the%20gym%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20way%20to%20promote%20themselves%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20local%20community%20they%20were%20a%20part%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20member%20of%20my%20gym%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20dog%20lover%2C%20told%20me%20about%20Mrs%20Lama.%20So%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20went%20and%20met%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alok%20recalls.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20truly%20inspired%20by%20what%20she%20had%20been%20doing%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20Every%20morning%2C%20she%20walks%208%20to%209%20kilometres%20to%20feed%20the%20strays.%20I%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20above%20and%20beyond%E2%80%99.%20While%20many%20people%20help%20animals%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20usually%20on%20a%20smaller%20scale.%20She%20was%20doing%20something%20extraordinary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20then%20and%20there%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20support%20her.%20Beyond%20the%20event%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20donate%20rice%20for%20the%20animals.%20The%20event%20itself%20was%20a%20success%2C%20and%20people%20also%20donated%20food%20and%20medication%20for%20the%20dogs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlok%E2%80%99s%20gym%20in%20Siliguri%20recently%20hosted%20a%20fundraiser%20to%20support%20Chandrika%E2%80%99s%20work.%20The%20concept%20was%20simple%3A%20for%20every%20pull-up%20that%20a%20participant%20completed%20during%20the%20event%2C%20a%20small%20donation%20would%20be%20made%20towards%20Indie%20RTR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20community%20and%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20strays%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alok%20explains.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20was%20modest%2C%20but%20we%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20with%20the%20response.%20The%20event%20was%20a%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20event%20not%20only%20raised%20funds%20but%20also%20educated%20people%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20caring%20for%20street%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrika%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20QR%20codes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Chandrika%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20become%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20many%20street%20animals%20in%20the%20area.%20But%20even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20her%20hus