ut%20the%20support%20of%20its%20corporate%20partners.%20Chennai%20Willingdon%20Corporate%20Foundation%20(CWCF)%2C%20Surveysparrow%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Lennox%20India%20Technology%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20funding%20the%20distribution%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275250%2Fdelhi-nest-man-builds-bird-bamboo-homes-trains-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enest%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ensuring%20the%20continued%20growth%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20acknowledges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20communities%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20corporate%20partnerships%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20source%20of%20funding%2C%20Ganeshan%20stresses%20that%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20true%20success%20lies%20in%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20involvement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20impact%20comes%20from%20students%2C%20families%2C%20and%20communities%20coming%20together%20to%20make%20this%20project%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrevious%20generations%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20sparrows%2C%20but%20today%E2%80%99s%20generation%20is%20less%20aware%20of%20how%20vital%20they%20are%20for%20human%20survival.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20general%20public%20often%20lacks%20the%20time%20or%20interest%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20significance.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20schools%2C%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20explain%20the%20mission%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founder%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201152px)%20100vw%2C%201152px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ganeshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-05-at-22.32.15-1-1731592215-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaneshan%20focuses%20on%20schools%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20discovery%20the%20NGO%20made%20was%20that%20the%20reduction%20in%20sand%20in%20urban%20areas%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20the%20sparrow%20population%20decline.%20In%202020%2C%20at%20Revoor%20Padmanabha%20Chetty%20Matriculation%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20in%20Tiruvottiyur%2C%20the%20abundance%20of%20sand%20made%20it%20the%20perfect%20environment%20for%20sparrows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20installing%20100%20nest%20boxes%20on%20the%20school%20campus%2C%20the%20results%20were%20immediate.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20six%20months%2C%20most%20of%20the%20boxes%20were%20occupied%2C%20and%20today%2C%20100%25%20of%20the%20nest%20boxes%20are%20in%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20proudly%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20dedicate%20our%20time%20to%20conserving%20sparrows%20because%20as%20their%20population%20grows%2C%20they%20will%20help%20control%20mosquitoes%2C%20cockroaches%2C%20and%20other%20small%20insects%20that%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20Sparrows%20thrive%20close%20to%20human%20settlements%2C%20as%20they%20can%20only%20survive%20in%20temperatures%20that%20are%20ideal%20for%20us%2C%20not%20in%20extremes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20next%20generation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoodugal%20Trust%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20students.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20Prayukta%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20student%20from%20RPC%20Matriculation%20School%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20project%2C%20and%20he%20brought%20home%20a%20nest%20in%202022.%20We%20all%20helped%20in%20installing%20it%2C%20and%20it%20was%20amazing%20to%20watch%20sparrows%20take%20care%20of%20their%20young%20ones.%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20feeding%20them%20and%20observing%20their%20activities.%20I%20would%20love%20to%20continue%20this%20sparrow%20conservation%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20engaging%20students%20in%20hands-on%20projects%2C%20Koodugal%20is%20not%20only%20educating%20them%20about%20sparrow%20conservation%20but%20also%20improves%20their%20motor%20skills%2C%20concentration%2C%20and%20empathy.%20These%20activities%20have%20significantly%20reduced%20screen%20time%20and%20have%20helped%20children%20develop%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Ganeshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20future%20plans%2C%20Ganeshan%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20sparrows%20a%20common%20sight%20across%20Chennai%20and%20expand%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20project%20to%20more%20schools%20and%20gated%20communities.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20reach%201%2C00%2C000%20families%20and%20distribute%20more%20nest%20boxes%20in%2010%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3